(19, 'SAVANNAH', 'Savannah is a wool hand knit and hand dyed top that will spice up your wardrobe with a pop of sunny color. It is a great piece to throw on when you want to be stylish and comfortable at the same time, and it can be paired with almost anything.\r\n\r\nThe traditional boatneck T-shirt design is updated with cutout sleeves that show off your shoulders. This style is very flattering on any body type. Made from a rustic, yet soft 100% wool yarn, Savannah can be worn on its own, or layered over a tank top or long sleeve shirt in cooler weather. It''s a great way to show off some skin in a very modest way.\r\n\r\nThe top is hand painted in an ombre effect, fading from a golden yellow at the top, to rust, to robins egg blue at the hem. Because this top is hand made from start to finish, it is truly one of a kind.', 335, 'Sand/Rust/Robbins Egg Multi', '100% Wool', 'Hand wash cool, dry flat or dry clean.', 'This top typically fits sizes S-L', '-20 inches from neck to hemline-40 inches around waist-8.5 inch sleeve opening-11 inch neck opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="PKZBGF2J86J7L"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'wool SS14 sweaters'),
(20, 'NORA', 'Savannah is a wool hand knit and hand dyed top that will spice up your wardrobe with a pop of sunny color. It is a great piece to throw on when you want to be stylish and comfortable at the same time, and it can be paired with almost anything.\r\n\r\nThe traditional boatneck T-shirt design is updated with cutout sleeves that show off your shoulders. This style is very flattering on any body type. Made from a rustic, yet soft 100% wool yarn, Savannah can be worn on its own, or layered over a tank top or long sleeve shirt in cooler weather. It''s a great way to show off some skin in a very modest way.\r\n\r\nIntroducing Nora, a wool hand knit and hand dyed top, perfect for the modern day explorer. A great layering piece that provides an ideal touch of warmth on overcast days or chilly evenings.\r\n\r\nThis top features a boatneck style with ribbed hem and sleeve detail. Made from a rustic, yet soft 100% wool yarn. Nora is a simple yet structured top that can be dressed up or down depending on the days adventure.\r\n\r\nHand-painted with subtle striping at the sleeves, hem and neckline. Nora features natural tones of robins egg blue, taupe and rust that blend to create beautiful color transitions. Because this top is hand made from start to finish it is truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 305, 'Rust, Taupe, Robbins EggMulti', '100% Wool', 'Hand Wash Cool, Lay Flat to Dry or Dry Clean', 'This top typically fits sizes S-M', '-19 inches from neck to hemline\n-37 inches around waist\n-11 inch sleeve opening\n-14 inch neck opening\n', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="R75P99H3M8LVG"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'wool SS14 sweaters'),
(21, 'HOPE', 'Hope-- a wool hand knit and hand dyed top, perfect for the modern day explorer. A great layering piece that provides an ideal touch of warmth on overcast days or chilly evenings.\r\n\r\nThis top features a boatneck style with ribbed hem and sleeve detail. Made from a rustic, yet soft 100% wool yarn. Hope is a simple yet structured top that can be dressed up or down depending on the day''s adventure.\r\n\r\nHand-painted with subtly blending stripes at the sleeves, hem and neckline. Hope features natural tones of pistachio green, brown and gold that melt together to create beautiful color transitions. Because this top is hand made from start to finish it is truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 305, 'Pistachio, Taupe, Sand', '100% Wool', 'Hand Wash Cool, Lay Flat to Dry or Dry Clean', 'This top typically fits sizes M-L', '-20.5 inches from neck to hemline\n-40 inches around waist\n-11 inch sleeve opening\n-11.5 inch neck opening\n', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="CSE7GGQ6RYKY2"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'wool SS14 sweaters'),
(22, 'DAHLIA', 'Dahlia is a dramatic top that will make a statement whether you are coming or going. This elegant, swingy top is cropped at just the right spot. Perfect for pairing with a high-waisted separate of your choice, or layering over a dress.\r\n\r\nThe center back and front of this top feature a contrasting reverse-knit panel accentuated by a complementary color. The open back is a U-shaped cutout with a ribbed strap which rests delicately above the shoulder blades.\r\n\r\nMade from a luxurious single ply 100% silk yarn. Dahlia can be worn on its own or layered, and with a swingy drape it will flatter any body type.\r\n\r\nHand-painted in a color-blocked style, the side panels fade from a light mauve at the shoulders to a dark, rich tone below. The front and back contrast panels are dyed in a light silvery blue, which blends with the mauve to create delicate shades of rose and lavender. The sheen of the silk adds multidimensional tones that are a must-see close up.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 368, 'Mauve Taupe, Cool Lavender', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'This top can fit sizes S-L\nNote: It will be very loose and drapey on a size S, and will be more fitted and cropped on a size L', '-19 inches from shoulder to hemline\n-43 inches around waist\n-11 inch sleeve opening\n-13 inch neck opening\n-8 inch diameter back cutout', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="Y6EP8EC35CCFU"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', 'SOLD', 'silk SS14 sweaters'),
(23, 'LILY', 'Lily is a dramatic top that will make a statement whether you are coming or going. This elegant, swingy top is cropped at just the right spot. Perfect for pairing with a high-waisted separate of your choice, or layering over a dress.\r\n\r\nThe center back and front of this top feature a contrasting reverse-knit panel accentuated by a complementary color. The open back is a U-shaped cutout with a ribbed strap which rests delicately above the shoulder blades.\r\n\r\nMade from a luxurious single ply 100% silk yarn. Lily can be worn on its own or layered, and with a swingy drape it will flatter any body type.\r\n\r\nHand-painted in a color-blocked style, with rust colored body and contrast panels of robins egg blue. The sheen of the silk adds multidimensional tones that are a must-see close up.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 368, 'Rust, Robbins Egg', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'This top can fit sizes S-L\nNote: It will be very loose and drapey on a size S, and will be more fitted and cropped on a size L', '-19 inches from shoulder to hemline\n-43 inches around waist\n-11 inch sleeve opening\n-13 inch neck opening\n-8 inch diameter back cutout', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="GKW3DU8M83YT2"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', 'SOLD', 'silk SS14 sweaters'),
(24, 'ADA', 'Ada is a tank top that you will never want to take off. The silk is soft and luxurious next to your skin. It''s a fantastic layering piece, but Ada also knows how to stand alone.\r\n\r\nThis tank top features a flattering high neck line in the front and a medium scoop in the back. It is a longer tank top and can also be classified as a "tunic." Ada flaunts an A-line silhouette that maintains its length on the sides while exhibiting an arching hemline.\r\n\r\nMade from a luxurious single ply 100% silk yarn. Its slightly more form-fitting A-line silhouette gives the body a nice shape while remaining comfortable throughout the bodice. Thick straps and a high neck give flattering coverage, while the scoop back provides an opportunity to show off the shoulders.\r\n\r\nHand-painted in an organic, abstract and subtly psychedelic wave pattern with colors of pistachio, turquoise, sea-foam and cobalt blue.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 244, 'Pistachio, Turquoise, Sea-foam and Cobalt blue', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'This top can fit sizes M', '-22 inches from middle neck to middle hemline-23 inches from underarm to tip of hem at sides-31 inches around waist-7 inch sleeve opening-8 inch neck opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="TS4TQGW26DKUY"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'silk SS14 sweaters'),
(25, 'GEORGINA', 'Introducing Georgina, an incredibly versatile silk hand knit and hand-dyed top. You can wear this top anywhere and it makes a perfect transition piece from day to night.\r\n\r\nThis top features a boatneck style with ribbed hem and sleeve detail. Made from a luxurious single ply 100% silk yarn. Georgina drapes with ease and elegance and flatters any body type.\r\n\r\nHand-painted in an ombre style moving from sea green/robins egg blue to a rich sandy gold. Because this top is hand made from start to finish it is truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California\r\n', 318, 'Sea-Green/ Robbins Egg, Sand', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'This top typically fits sizes M-L', '-19 inches from neck to hemline\n-44 inches around waist\n-13 inch sleeve opening\n-15 inch neck opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="89VEN2ABJM84L"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'silk SS14 sweaters'),
(26, 'ELIZA', 'Perfect for those who prefer solid colors, our Eliza tank top looks superb with many skin tones and pairs very well with a plethora of other colors and tones.\r\n\r\nThis tank top features a flattering scoop neck line in the front and a deep scoop in the back. It is a longer tank top and can also be classified as a "tunic." Eliza offers an A-line silhouette that maintains its length on the sides while exhibiting an arching hemline.\r\n\r\nMade from a luxurious single ply 100% silk yarn. Its slightly more form-fitting A-line silhouette gives the body a nice shape while remaining comfortable throughout the bodice. Thick straps and a tasteful scoop neck offer flattering coverage, while the scoop back provides an opportunity to show off the shoulders.\r\n\r\nHand-painted a solid rust color, this silk top offers tonal variations due to the multidimensional nature of the silk.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 230, 'Rust', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'This top can fit sizes S-L\nNote: On size S top will be looser, and size L top will be slightly more body conscious ', '-19.5 inches from middle neck to middle hemline\n-19 inches from underarm to tip of hem at sides\n-32 inches around waist\n-11.5 inch sleeve opening\n-8.5 inch neck opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="SPBD95CRZA3KC"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'silk SS14 sweaters'),
(27, 'EVELYN', 'Evelyn is a 100% silk hand knit and hand dyed top that will add elegance and sophistication to any outfit you pair it with. It is a great top to wear to work with an oversize cardigan, and at night remove the cardigan and you''re ready for a night on the town! The silk is so soft and luxurious next to your skin, you will never want to take it off.\r\n\r\nThe traditional boatneck T-shirt design is updated with cutout sleeves that show off your shoulders while providing flattering coverage at the same time. Made from a gorgeous and soft spun silk yarn, Evelyn can be worn on its own, or layered over a tank top or long sleeve shirt in cooler weather. It''s a great way to show off some skin in a tasteful way.\r\n\r\nThe top is hand painted with a background of pistachio green. The upper and lower portions of the shirt are accented with subtle blended stripes of rust, gold, brown and blue, and some delicate white lines created through a resist dyeing technique. Because this top is hand made from start to finish, it is truly one of a kind.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 372, 'Rust, Sand, Taupe, Sage', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'This top typically fits sizes M-L', '-21 inches from neck to hemline\n-42 inches around waist\n-9 inch sleeve opening\n-11.5 inch neck opening.', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="UUWHNNHWMECHY"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'silk SS14 sweaters'),
(28, 'AMELIA', 'Introducing Amelia, an alpaca/silk blend hand knit and hand dyed top that is both comfortable and elegant at the same time. A great layering piece that provides an ideal touch of warmth on overcast days or chilly evenings.\r\n\r\nThis top features a boatneck style with a simple rolled edge, and ribbed hem and sleeves. The alpaca fiber lends the top an incredible softness and warmth, while the silk provides a delicate sheen.\r\n\r\nThe shirt is hand-painted with a robins egg blue background, and a detail of rust red along the neckline, sleeves and hem. Where the colors meet, they blend to create an infinite variation of subtle tones. Because this top is hand made from start to finish it is truly one of a kind.', 312, 'Rust, Robbins Egg, Taupe', 'Fiber: 80% Alpaca 20% Silk', ' Care: Hand Wash Cool, Dry Flat or Dry Clean', 'This top typically fits sizes XS-S', '- 18.5 inches from neck to hemline- 33 inches around waist- 8 inch sleeve opening- 12.5 inch neck opening.', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="5SM2GJQN6HZGJ"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'alpaca/silk SS14 sweaters'),
(29, 'FLORENCE', 'Florence-- a new take on a super comfortable second skin tank top. Fantastic for summer days or nights no matter which coast you are on.\r\n\r\nThis tank top features a flattering high neck line in the front and a medium scoop in the back. It is a longer tank top and can also be classified as a "tunic." Florence flaunts an A-line silhouette that maintains its length on the sides while exhibiting an arching hemline. The alpaca/silk fabrication clings close to skin and almost makes you forget you''re wearing anything at all.\r\n\r\nMade from a luxurious plied alpaca/silk yarn. Its form-fitting A-line silhouette gives the body a nice shape while remaining comfortable throughout the bodice. Comfortable straps and a high neck give flattering coverage, while the scoop back provides an opportunity to show off the shoulders.\r\n\r\nHand-painted in an organic, abstract and subtly psychedelic wave pattern with colors of rust, golden yellow and pale mauve.\r\n\r\nMade in Oakland, California', 238, 'Rust, Sand, Pale Mauve', 'Fiber: 80% Alpaca 20% Silk', ' Care: Hand Wash Cool, Dry Flat or Dry Clean', 'This top can fit sizes XS-S', '-22.5 inches from middle neck to middle hemline-22 inches from underarm to tip of hem at sides-25 inches around waist-9 inch sleeve opening-8 inch neck opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="9YTMSQSPEX69C"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', 'SOLD', 'alpaca/silk SS14 sweaters'),
(31, 'LYDIA BEACH', 'No matter where you are, this Lydia Drop-Stitch Scarf will remind you of where the beach meets the gentle ocean waves. The luster of the silk provides a luxurious way to add a touch of shine to any ensemble day or night. Silk also possesses the unique quality of keeping the wearer warm or cool depending on the situation. Delicate like a spider''s web, you could sped an hour admiring the subtle color gradients that make up the body of the scarf. ', 130, 'Sand, Robbin''s Egg Blue', 'Fiber: 100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'Free Size', 'Length: 60 in. approx. Width: 8 in. approx.', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="4VM6WR9CCJCHA"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', 'SOLD', 'silk SS14 scarves'),
(32, 'LYDIA DESERT', 'Examining our Lydia Desert Drop-Stitch Scarf will whisk you away to the world''s most intoxicating deserts. Here a pale blush and gold are married to mimic the melting sand-blown landscapes. Again, another simple way to add just the right amount of luxury and luster to your attire whether your meeting your friend''s for brunch or heading into the office. Silk keeps the body cool in the heat and warm when it''s cold.', 135, 'Pale Pink, Gold', '100% silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'Free Size', 'Length: 65 in approx. Width: 8 in approx.', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"><input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="VNBWACV7CJJ5W"><input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"><img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"></form>', 'SOLD', 'silk SS14 scarves'),
(33, 'LYDIA WOODLAND', 'This Lydia Woodland Drop-Sitch Scarf is for the lover of deeper wood-like colors. A beautiful strawberry rust combines with a plum wood tone to bring a bit of interest to a neutral color scheme. These two colors offer an excellent complement to tan, black or brown without being one of those colors themselves! Admire the multidimensional nature of the silk next to the flame at your candlelit dinner.', 130, 'Rust, Purple', '100% silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'Free Size', 'Length: 60 in approx. Width: 8 in approx.  ', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"><input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="4VM6WR9CCJCHA"><input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"><img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"></form>', 'SOLD', 'silk SS14 scarves'),
(34, 'MAE', 'Mae is our updated take on a very classic sweater shape. Its crewneck and Â¾ sleeves are unexpectedly accentuated by sheer paneling across the decolletage and shoulder blades as well as down the center arm. ItÂ’s a fantastic transitional piece between day and night. The sheer panels create a subtle magic on the body in that they are not immediately recognizable or obvious at first glance, and are much more appreciated upon intimate inspection. The color was inspired by one of the many fantastic rock walls in The Grand Canyon. ', 268, 'Ombre Rust Red', '98% Merino Wool 2% Wool Blend', 'Handwash with Woolite or other mild detergent, gently squeeze out excess water, lay flat and smooth to dry.', 'XS', '30" bust 15" neck to hem 15&quot 3/4 sleeves', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="F9JHFEMT78GWQ"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Wool Sweaters'),
(35, 'ADELINE', 'This version of our sheer panel sweater features a full length sleeve and longer sweater body. It melts perfectly from a tawny peach through a rich but vibrant rosy tone and finishes by fading into a perfect plum. These sweaters bring the wearer effortless luxury. Pair with a pair of trousers by day and a dramatic floor length skirt for night. The sheer paneling on the arms, chest and back gives this relaxed sweater the added mystery it needs to make it one of your most coveted wardrobe items.', 324, 'Ombre Purple Rust Red', '98% Merino Wool, 2% wool blend', 'Hand wash with Woolite or other mild detergent, squeeze out water gently, lay flat and smooth to dry.', 'S', '32" bust 16" neck to hem 22" sleeve length.', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="29SEXXTHS4FNW"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Wool Sweaters'),
(36, 'PEARL', 'The colors and patterns on this 100% Tussah Silk top were inspired by the movement and colors of Antelope Canyon. Pearl features a drop shoulder, long sleeves and a beautifully crafted open back rounded diamond shape, crowned by a twisted knit panel. A perfect and flattering way to show off some skin. The multidimensional nature of the silk is enhanced by the light, neutral, barely-there tones. Its swingy, cropped silhouette hangs perfectly over skinny jeans or a full length skirt of your pairing. Made by hand, for a one of a kind woman.', 290, 'Tan Lilac Grey-Purple', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'L', '56" Bust 16" Neck to Hem', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="JMXJHULUQ479U"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Sweaters Silk'),
(37, 'BEATRICE', 'Our romantic swingy, cropped open back sweater set in more vibrant tones for those who prefer to Ã‚Â“make an entrance.Ã‚Â” In tones of violet, mauve, rose and champagne Beatrice keeps all eyes on you. Inspired by Agate rocks and canyon details Beatrice pairs well with high-waisted riding pants, jeans, trousers and more. 100% silk gives comfort next to skin, while the whimsical opening in the back provides just the right way to show off some skin subtly and comfortably. Destined to become an instant favorite of yours for seasons to come.', 282, 'Golden-Yellow Purple Mauve', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'S', '44" Bust Ã‚Â 14" Neck to Hem', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="5SQ8PD2EWBH3C"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Silk Sweaters'),
(38, 'ANNIE', 'This one is for the neutral tone lovers-- we know youÃ‚Â’re out there. Our one of a kind crewneck sweater with sheer panels in an exquisite brown palette. In this hand-dyed one of a kind classic you will find tones of chocolate, amber, nutmeg and cinnamon. Inspired by the layers of rock memorialized in the The Grand Canyon, the sheer panels invite your skin to become part of the layers, turning heads from all directions around you. Merino wool sits neck to skin making you wonder why on earth you wear anything else.', 336, 'Ombre Chocolate Tan', '98% merino Wool 2% Wool Blend', 'Hand wash with Woolite or other mild detergent, gently squeeze out excess water, lay flat and smooth to dry.', 'L', '38" Bust 17" Neck to Hem 25" Sleeves', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="5BV4XF8BCUMTL"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Sweaters Wool'),
(39, 'VIOLA', 'Viola takes our sheer panel sweater to the final glimpses of canyon light before the darkness. Set with antique mauve and a cabernet chocolate tone it would look good with any skin tone. A piece that moves you easily and comfortably through your busy day and into your plans for that evening. The hand-dyed nature of this one of a kind sweater offers coloration variations that could be admired endlessly. A tall cuff makes it easy to push back sleeves when necessary-- youÃ‚Â’re a pioneering woman after all.', 332, 'Monochromatic Ombre Mauve', '98% Merino Wool 2% Wool Blend', 'Handwash with Woolite or other mild detergent, gently squeeze to remove excess water, lay flat and smooth to dry.', 'M', ' 34" Bust 17" Neck to Hem 24" Sleeves', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="4S9TVZDHCCWXJ"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Wool Sweaters'),
(40, 'JULIET', 'This long-sleeve sweater features tiny little drop-stitches to perfectly show off sneak peeks of skin on the wearer. A romantic silhouette featuring a wide boatneck that can go on or off the shoulder and arching hemline provide just the right dose of bohemia and luxury. Made from our 100% Tussah Silk, the subtle colors blend with a silky sheen reminiscent of a southwest desert at dawn. Throw it on over a dress for effortless dressing, but nonetheless royal. ', 248, 'Lilac Rose Golden-Yellow', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'M', '40" Bust Â 19" Neck to Hem Â 15" Neck Opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="WZ72AE2JZZG9J"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Silk Sweaters'),
(41, 'ROXIE', 'Roxie is your next go to sweater. Made entirely from Tussah Silk, it offers extraordinary comfort next to skin. Its cropped and swingy silhouette is extremely flattering worn with highwaisted skirts and pants, even jeans. Throw it on over a dress for a little touch of effortless bohemia. This one of a kind sweater was inspired by Banded Agate and the colors of The Grand Canyon at Alpenglow. This special handmade design will bring just the right amount of subtle luxury to its wearer whether youÃƒÂƒÃ‚ÂƒÃƒÂ‚Ã‚Â‚ÃƒÂƒÃ‚Â‚ÃƒÂ‚Ã‚Â’re dressing up or down. The drop-shoulder design features a roomy body and a twisted knit panel across the shoulder blades, which crowns a rounded diamond open-back shape just below. DonÃƒÂƒÃ‚ÂƒÃƒÂ‚Ã‚Â‚ÃƒÂƒÃ‚Â‚ÃƒÂ‚Ã‚Â’t forget to spend time in sunlight examining the blending swirls of color enhanced by the multidimensional nature of the silk.', 284, 'Red Lilac Rose Orange', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'M', '50" Bust 14" Neck to Hem', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="24AWXQME7E92J"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Sweaters Silk'),
(42, 'GRACE', 'A vibrant version of our romantic drop-stitch sweater in hues of champagne, garnet and magenta. This extremely soft 100% silk sweater is flowy and full body, with a subtly arching hemline. Perfect for an afternoon picnic in a field of wildflowers or a more formal event that goes on long after dark. Silk has the ability to keep the wearer warm or cool depending on conditions. Why decide between being comfortable and looking luxurious when you can do both!', 250, 'Red Magenta Champagne', '100% Silk', 'Dry Clean Only', 'L', '48" Bust  19" Neck to Hem  14" Neck Opening', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"> <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"> <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="DZEVXR92GRN4N"> <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1"> </form>', '', 'FW14 Silk Sweaters'),
