(115, 'SMALL MACRAME BACK TANK', 'This small silk and wool tank top is truly one of a kind and truly comfortable. Our lightweight wool and silk blend together in this plied yarn to keep your body the perfect temperature as well as dry through Spring and Summer days or nights. A fantastic layering piece for all the color mixers and lovers out there. The top features a high well covering front while the back, featuring macrame does the talking. A prefect way to flatter your backside!\n\nThis tank top features a wool and silk plied yarn obtained from an individual odd lot seller online. This tank top began as a strand of that yarn that Leah hand knit on her manual knitting machine. After knitting, she sewed the pieces together and knotted the cords into an intricate design on the back.\n\nThe top was then soaked and hand dyed by Ailee using a special technique. After, this tank top was individually steamed to set the dyes so that the tank top will remain colorfast for you, the customer. It was then soaked and conditioned, and finally blocked to size!', 248, 'Ombre Mint Tan', 'Wool and Silk Blend', 'Hand Wash Cool\nReshape\nLay Flat to Dry\n\nDry Clean', 'S', 'Length: 13 1/2" (34cm) from neck to hem\nWidth: 30" (76cm) around bust\nNeck: 8 1/2" (21cm) neck opening\nArmhole: 8" (20cm) armhole depth', '<form target="paypal" action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">\n<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">\n<input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="3DJXPUZ9XNFSC">\n<input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_cart_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">\n<img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">\n</form>\n', '', 'Wool/Silk SS15 Tank-Tops'),
